<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>In a country named Herb Land, several princes are preparing to the great competition, in the end of which one of them will become a king! But you, the young hero of the game (who also happens to be a prince), should know one important thing: if a prince doesn't have success with girls, he won't win the competition! And so, your quest for the crown and for the attention of the fairer sex begins...
                  <br><br>The game is a mixture of simulation, adventure, and role-playing. It can also be described as a table RPG. You compete against three other princes, and must have more success with the game's several main female characters in order to become a king. Your actions in the game are determined by the roll of dice. It will tell you at what time of the week you'll be able to begin your turn, how many steps you take on the world map, how much damage you do in battles, and so on. When you visit a town, you should go to see the girls and take quests from them. Those can include the elimination of an evil monster or a simple fetch task. You will also fight against the other princes in tournament mode.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Set in the world of sword and sorcery, a simulation RPG "Love! Compete generously" is the slogan of the prince, there is also a love element to participate in the election to choose the next king. Communicate with a girl who is also habit also two personality trait of 12 people in one of the four princes, voters choose a king, players will win the hearts of girls and the seat of the king.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective.</li>
			<li>2D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Medieval Fantasy theme.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

